# ProofMeta — Cursor rules

- Single source of truth: `PROOFMETA_ANWEISUNG.md`. Do not contradict it; propose edits there first.
- Protocol only: no mandatory payment, storage, or chain in core code paths.
- Canonical schemas: `packages/spec/*.schema.json` (draft-07).
- Status values are only: OPEN, PENDING, GRANTED, DENIED, REVOKED.
- Prefer small, spec-driven changes; Apache-2.0 applies to this repo.
